Our guide made the trip interesting and informative. In Fatima we had plenty of time to enjoy the Sanctuary and local sights. The duration and price of the tour was perfectly matched!

fields.title: Thank you so much!!!
fields.short_text: I have been to many cities in Portugal and I can confidently say that Fatima is the pearl of Portugal. The town is very nice, with many cozy cafes and stores. It was here that I tasted the most delicious wine of my life! The guide turned out to be a good man and a professional.

fields.title: Well done
fields.short_text: The Fatima Sanctuary is one of the most impressive places I have ever visited. I have never photographed so much and cannot believe that such structures could have been built by humans. Separately, I would like to mention the service.

fields.title: Best beaches ever!
fields.short_text: Since childhood I love water and love swimming in the seas and oceans, so this excursion was a real paradise for me. I was especially impressed by the Grand Beach, which according to the guide is the largest on the coast of Sintra. I would also like to thank him for kindly agreeing to take pictures of me. Perfect day!

fields.title: Thank you to the One Day Tours team!
fields.short_text: For photography lovers, I definitely recommend booking this tour as it offers stunning views for photos. I haven't seen such beauty in a long time! The water is clean and clear and every beach in Sintra has something unusual to offer. The kids especially loved it.

fields.title: Just a comfortable trip!
fields.short_text: The service was amazing! The driver was very polite and professional, and the guide was a real expert on the history and culture of the region. The trip was comfortable, the car was clean and air conditioned. Free water and pleasant conversation made the trip even better. Thank you, guys!

fields.title: Wonderful!
fields.short_text: We booked the 10 hour tour to the military town of Elvas and enjoyed it! The fortress of Santa Luzia immediately impressed us with its monumental view. We walked around the bastions and enjoyed the views of the surrounding area. This place made us feel the significance of military architecture and made us think. A wonderful cultural enlightenment!

fields.title: Unexpected wow!
fields.short_text: Wonderful excursion to the The Church Of Our Lady Of Assumption and the fortresses of Santa Luzia and Elvas, which offer picturesque views for photo shoots. Thanks to the guide for kindly agreeing to take photos of us. There are no remarks to the service, and the excursion itself was quite interesting. We learned a lot of new things. 10/10!

fields.title: Best historical experience ever!
fields.short_text: The tour to Elvas was just wonderful. Everything was enjoyable and the history of each building was really interesting and unusual. I would like to single out the local pastries. The smell of it spreads all over the street and the taste is just wonderful. We were very tired, but the comfortable bus and wonderful humor of the guide leveled the fatigue.

fields.title: Day in Elvas
fields.short_text: Many thanks to the organizers of the tour. The car was spotlessly clean, and many thanks to the driver for agreeing to stop at a personal request and giving us the opportunity to take beautiful photos. The guide was a good man and recommended a really awesome place for traditional Portuguese food with inexpensive prices. 5 stars to you, friends!

fields.title: Great day trip with onedaytours
fields.short_text: The site is a service I will continue to use in the future. We were picked up directly from the hotel and driven in a comfortable car with air conditioning, which was very helpful in the heat. All the way the guide told interesting historical stories about the city of Elvas and even shared experiences from his personal life. The cherry on the cake of the tour was the local desserts. My wife will remember the pie with almonds and honey for the rest of her life!

fields.title: Muito Lindo! Obrigado!
fields.short_text: The tour is a real find! Republic Square turned out to be a lively and colorful place where you could feel the real atmosphere of Elvas. We observed the life of the citizens, enjoyed the local cafes and took lots of photos. Despite the military history it is the perfect place to relax and unwind. 100% recommended!

fields.title: Thank you!
fields.short_text: I am from France, but I have long dreamed of visiting Lisbon. Thanks to the possibility of excursions in different languages, I saw and heard a lot of interesting things and even had time to taste local food. Thank you very much for this journey.

fields.title: Awesome experience!
fields.short_text: For such a small price you can fully immerse yourself in the history of Lisbon and all its secrets. The tour was very well planned. We had time to eat and see the ancient architecture of Lisbon and we also had the opportunity to take photos.

fields.title: My review
fields.short_text: These were unforgettable 4 hours in my life. I enjoyed looking at the sights of Lisbon with great pleasure. Here you will find entertainment for every taste. You can also eat local food because there are a lot of restaurants.

fields.title: Very good experience
fields.short_text: I thoroughly enjoyed all the beauties of Lisbon and thanks to good conditions and kind guides, I completely immersed myself in this historical city. The architecture and atmosphere do not let go for a second.

fields.title: Just excelent
fields.short_text: It was fantastic travel! During these 4 hours we managed to see many interesting places such as the squares of Restauradores, King Peter the 4th, and Figueira and even had time to eat deliciously in local restaurants. For this small price, you will experience an unforgettable trip to Lisbon.

fields.title: Super nice
fields.short_text: Lisbon is a very beautiful city with a lot of history and attractions.

fields.title: Beautiful experience!
fields.short_text: Thanks to the guide's kindness and interesting stories, we learned a lot about the sights of Lisbon.

fields.title: Best daytrip ever!
fields.short_text: Thanks very much to One Day Tours for giving me that opportunity to see the beautiful architecture Monastery of Batalha. I would like to say about the price. Nice price and available to everyone. For this price, you will get a lot of emotions and adventures. You definitely won't regret.

fields.title: Unique esperience
fields.short_text: This trip was excellent! Everything is thought out to the smallest details. Most of all we remembered the Batalha Monastery architecture. The tombstone statue of the king, the dome, the gargoyles are made at the highest level. Even today everything looks gorgeous.

fields.title: We enjoyed this trip!
fields.short_text: Thanks very much to the driver for this journey. My dream was to see the Holy Town of Fatima and I wasnt disappointed. In Fatima, in several different places you can feel very close to the sacred stories. You can see several monuments, places of prayer, and a large number of symbolic references.

fields.title: Lovely trip
fields.short_text: I haven't had this much fun of traveling for a long time. Everything was at the highest level. While traveling on the van, the guide told us interesting stories about these places. And then we could see it with our own eyes. You will definitely not get bored on this excursion.

fields.title: Good experience for reasonable price
fields.short_text: If you want to relax from big city noises its a best choice. In this trip you can relax and see great architecture and monuments. We also tried a local tasty food. Fantastic travel!

fields.title: Fantastic Portugal with one day tours!
fields.short_text: Despite the duration of the excursion, we did not have time to notice how it ended. Everything was so interesting that I didnt want to waste a minute. I photographed everything I could. I recommend everyone to go there.

fields.title: This trip was fantastic!
fields.short_text: We have never been in the Fatima and Batalha until this travel. It was very interesting to see the architecture of our ancestors. Architecture was awesome and also I can mentioned Batalha market where you can taste rare exotic fruits and friendly residents who will gladly welcome you.

fields.title: Perfect trip!
fields.short_text: I would like to note about comfortable buses with air conditioners. Despite the duration of the trip we saw a lot of interesting places with their unforgettable architectures. My favourite was Fatima. Its a very interesting place with a long history.

fields.title: Best present to your parents!
fields.short_text: Its was a very interesting travel. Also I would say about opportunity for disabled people. My father cant go and he always dreamed to see Monastery of Batalha. Thanks to the opportunity to take people with disabilities. With you his dream becomes reality.

fields.title: Amazing trip
fields.short_text: It was unforgettable trip! I would like to note the amazing Gothic exterior of the Batalha monastery. Here you will find entertainment for every taste. You can eat according to your taste because there are a lot of restaurants near the monastery. Or you can plunge into the history of this monastery along with interesting stories from a guide.

fields.title: My sincere thanks to One Day Tours.
fields.short_text: Trip was great. I would like to note the comfortable buses. We were with our 2 small children. And thanks to the buses, a good driver and interesting stories from guide. Children were calm the entire trip without any problems and were very pleased. Thank you from all our family.

fields.title: Thanks very much to the One Days Tours!
fields.short_text: Perfect trip. The architecture, the food, the excursion, the guides, the beautiful views just blew my mind. It was nice to see the place where the Virgin Mary appeared.

fields.title: Awesome trip with this company!
fields.short_text: I would like to tell about my experience about this tour. Monastery of Batalha and the Holy Town of Fatima inspired me to learn more about this places. It took me back to the 14th century. I don't know how people in those days managed to build such masterpieces of architecture.

fields.title: The monastery of Batalha is simply stunning!
fields.short_text: The architecture is breathtaking and the views all around are like being in a fairy tale. Fatima was touching, my husband especially liked the site of the apparition of the Virgin Mary. A worthy excursion for a reasonable price. We recommend it to everyone!

fields.title: We enjoyed! Thank you!
fields.short_text: Thank you One Day Tours for the wonderful opportunity to see beautiful places and for the quality service. The guide was interesting to listen to. Especially surprised Santarem with its Gothic buildings that took me back in time. I will definitely come back here!

fields.title: Great memories and emotions
fields.short_text: A great tour for architecture lovers. The monastery of Batalha left unforgettable impressions with its design and grandeur. Special thanks to the driver for the safe ride and clean bus. I am a perfectionist and I was really impressed.

fields.title: This tour surprised me! Thank you, guys!
fields.short_text: The trip was amazing! The Batalha Monastery is one of the most beautiful places I have seen. The town itself was also impressive with its nature and aesthetics. But my taste buds enjoyed Fatima more. Here I tasted the most delicious seafood at a local cafe recommended by my guide. Thank you!

fields.title: Thank you, we enjoyed this trip!
fields.short_text: The service was excellent. The guide was very knowledgeable about the route and history of the places. The driver was polite and neat. Batalha, Fatima and Santaren are the first cities I have visited, but I am already starting to like Portugal! It really has beautiful nature and unpretentious architecture. Fabulous!

fields.title: 5 stars!
fields.short_text: I'm not a big fan of European countries, but Portugal hit my heart. I was surprised by the combination of religion and architecture, and Fatima impressed me with its tranquility. The water and air conditioning in the car added to the comfort.

fields.title: Great tour to visit with kids
fields.short_text: Took the excursion with kids and was very worried that it would be hard for them to endure the 10 hour tour. However, thanks to One Day Tours, the trip was easy and relaxing. I personally want to mention the scenery of Santarem. Whoever is planning to visit it, don't forget to bring your camera!

fields.title: Superb day!
fields.short_text: My girlfriend and I like active vacations, so we often book excursions. This is the first time we have used One Day Tours and we are completely satisfied with the service. The meeting at the hotel and the return transfer were a real treat. The driver kindly agreed to drive slower so we could capture the stunning views along the way. The tour itself was informative.

fields.title: Simply the best!
fields.short_text: When in Portugal, be sure to try the local pastries and their wine. The white was fantastic! The sights of Fatima are a sight to behold.... Here I felt calm and soulful atmosphere. However, we wouldn't have experienced this without the help of One Day Tours.

fields.title: Excellent service!!!
fields.short_text: The guide was a true professional, very enthusiastic and knowledgeable. The car was comfortable, with air conditioning and water, which you don't find every time. I advise everyone to visit Portugal in the spring, its fantastic!

fields.title: I am satisfied with the trip!
fields.short_text: The Batalha Monastery surprised with its architecture and history, and Fatima is a place full of spiritual meaning. Here we even had time to meditate and pray. Thanks to the guide and driver for agreeing to wait for us a bit.

fields.title: Excellent Portugal! Excellent guide!
fields.short_text: Santarem was a real discovery for me. The Gothic capital of Portugal impressed with its majestic buildings. Especially memorable was the church of Santa Maria de Graa with its stunning details. We took a year's worth of pictures.

fields.title: Recommend to everyone
fields.short_text: The nature at Cape Espichel is simply breathtaking. Incredible cliffs, ocean views and absolute silence make this place unique. The children now say every day that they want to go back. Great excursion!

fields.title: Thank you!
fields.short_text: Booked the Arrabida Natural Park & Cape Espichel Tour and didn't regret it one bit. We were particularly impressed with the park, namely its greenery and picturesque panoramas. It was a real oasis of tranquility and beauty. We took tons of beautiful photos and ended the day on a positive note. Thank you!

fields.title: Great experience!
fields.short_text: The service was top notch! The driver was very professional and caring. Twice during the trip he asked us if we had seasickness or if the cabin was stuffy. The trip was comfortable and without delays. 10/10!

fields.title: experienced traveller!
fields.short_text: I recommend everyone to visit the slope of Mount Arrabida and the Espichel estate. Besides the natural beauty, the cape surprised us with its historical sights. The monastery and the lighthouse added a special charm and variety to the trip. Thank you so much, guys for the wonderful opportunity!

fields.title: We loved this trip
fields.short_text: I love such secluded places. Cape Espichel was almost empty and this allowed me to fully enjoy nature and meditate. The weather was hot and the only thing that helped was bottled water. Very thoughtful, the quality service was amazing!

fields.title: We loved this trip
fields.short_text: I love such secluded places. Cape Espichel was almost empty and this allowed me to fully enjoy nature and meditate. The weather was hot and the only thing that helped was bottled water. Very thoughtful, the quality service was amazing!

fields.title: Dreams comes true!
fields.short_text: Fantastic views of the mountains and the sea in Arrabida Park. Real scenery like from a postcard. With my husband after the tour we decided to come another day and have a picnic. Portugal is a country that is definitely worth visiting at least once in a lifetime.

fields.title: Thanks for the experience
fields.short_text: The organization of the tour is 100 stars. The car was very comfortable and clean and most importantly with air conditioning and bottled water which were a lifesaver on a sunny day. The tour was informative and interesting. Next year I will come here with my parents.

fields.title: We enjoyed this tour
fields.short_text: 4 hours is the ideal length of the tour. During this time, my children and I didn't get tired, but we had time to learn a lot of new things. The guide was very attentive to our wishes and interests. Thank him very much for his advice on where to buy souvenirs at an adequate price. One Day Tours left a pleasant impression.

fields.title: Arrabida surprised us!
fields.short_text: Arrabida is a real gem. Breathtaking views, clean air and beautiful vegetation. The guide even agreed to take a few pictures of us. This place is a must see! A wonderful excursion for a reasonable price.

fields.title: Worst to try!
fields.short_text: Walking the trails of the Arrabida Park was wonderful. Lots of interesting trails and places to stop and rest. My wife especially liked the service. Everything went strictly according to schedule. We were picked up on time and visited all the planned places without any delays. I really liked this approach.

fields.title: Perfect day!
fields.short_text: Thanks One Day Tours for this journey. Service was excellent. Kind guide tell us about an incredible history of Obidos and Nazare.

fields.title: Great day trip!
fields.short_text: Amazing trip. Comfortable bus with air conditioners helps us to fully enjoy this incredible places. I would also like to mention the good guide who told and showed the whole history of these places. Most of all I remember Obidos with its incredible history and beauty. Here you can see Calle Direita, the delightful main street of Obidos, which has remained virtually unchanged since the Middle Ages.

fields.title: Best birthday ever!
fields.short_text: My wife arranged this trip for us in honor of my birthday and the gift did not disappoint. Good conditions, a bus with air conditioning and comfortable seats. We were able to see many of the sights of Obidos and even swim in the ocean on the beach of Nazar.

fields.title: Excellent journey!
fields.short_text: Thanks to comfortable buses guide, we really enjoyed the trip. Obidos is a very beautiful city with a lot of history and beautiful views. Here you can see ancient architecture and even try local food. For example, Ginjinha d'Obidos - delicious and sweet cherry the liqueur served in a chocolate cup is the perfect way to replenish your energy levels during a long day of sightseeing!

fields.title: Good service for good price
fields.short_text: The service was very good. The guides and driver are professionals. We saw the incredible architecture of Obidos and saw the beautiful views of Nazar, and also tried the local delicious food. Simply the best!

fields.title: Big day in great place
fields.short_text: Thanks to the One days tours team for the opportunity to visit these incredible places. The guide was very kind and told all the most interesting things and then we were able to see this beauty with our own eyes. Nazar is a charming city. Here you can swim in the ocean, see the sights and try local food. We visited the Sitiu district - the historic and charming district of Nazar, and also Fort Saint Miguel Arcanjou.Beautiful travel!

fields.title: Thanks so much to One Day Tours for this wonderful adventure
fields.short_text: I have never had such pleasure traveling before. I love the history of Portugal and wanted to see the beauty of Obidos and Nazar. The guide was very helpful and told me all the interesting things and answered all my questions. I saw the wonderful sights of Obidos such as Muralhas da Cidade, Porta da Vila and others. Some day I will go surfing to Nazare in my free time.

fields.title: It was a great trip!
fields.short_text: I have wanted to take this tour for a long time and the trip was totally worth it. We saw a lot of interesting places. I would like to make special mention of the markets of Obidos, where the locals will gladly welcome you and let you try incredible delicacies.

fields.title: The guide been fantastic! Thank you!
fields.short_text: The guide was amiable and shared interesting facts about the "Expo-98" exhibition. I especially liked the Vasco da Gama Tower and the Portuguese National Pavilion. Simply the best!

fields.title: Wonderful experience!
fields.short_text: I learned a lot of information from the guides about modern Lisbon. The guides are professionals and passionate about their work. I especially remember the information about the Portuguese architect Siza Vieira. Thank you for your guidance.

fields.title: 10/10 experience
fields.short_text: One Day Tours experiences are a great option to discover Lisbon from a different perspective. The time spent touring the Park of Nations flew by, and it was both enjoyable and educational. The guide's professionalism deserves special thanks. I learned a lot about the history of the "Expo-98" exhibition in 1998 and the Oriente railway station, which you won't hear about on other tours.

fields.title: Superb tour!
fields.short_text: he tour became even more enjoyable thanks to the guide, with whom I even became friends. I was especially impressed by the massive MEO Arena, the Portuguese National Pavilion, and of course, the Aquarium with its many exotic fish species. I highly recommend this company.

fields.title: Excellent!
fields.short_text: I enjoyed the tour of modern Lisbon! One Day Tours guide showed us the Park of Nations and the secret favorite spots of the locals. I was especially impressed by Santiago Calatrava's masterpiece, the vast Vasco da Gama shopping center. The guides managed to tell us a lot of historical and fun information.

fields.title: Thanks to the members of One Day Tours company for the best tour in the Park of Nations!
fields.short_text: The guides of this company stand out for their special friendliness and easy delivery of information. I liked the organization of showing Vasco da Gama places with the Oriente railway station and the Aquarium. Simply the best!

fields.title: Different Portugal :)
fields.short_text: With One Day Tours, we discovered a new part of Lisbon! Our guides are true professionals who showed and told many interesting stories about the Park of Nations and MEO Arena. We enjoyed the picturesque landscapes around the Tagus River, even during the walk. Awesome!

fields.title: Best of the best!
fields.short_text: My husband and I joined the One Day Tours excursion to Portugal's religious and historical centers, and we didn't regret it! The day started with the cozy town of Fatima, where we visited the Batalha Monastery. Portuguese architecture never ceases to impress me, especially in Nazare. Thanks to our guide for the informative conversation and interesting facts about each place.

fields.title: I highly recommend this companyit is simply the best!
fields.short_text: My child was thrilled with the One Day Tours excursion! The guides' organization was top-notch, and they managed to engage him with unchildish topics. Personally, I was delighted with the visit to Nazare, where we tried local delicacies and saw the ocean.

fields.title: Our Fatima tour
fields.short_text: We didn't know what to do on our last vacation day and decided to spend it wisely. I cant say enough good things about One Day Tours. From the moment I contacted them, they were responsive and accommodating. In 8 hours, we saw the holy places of Fatima and the Batalha Monastry and drove along a picturesque road to the small and charming town of Obidos. Besides seeing, we learned many stories about all things Portuguese. Thank you for your assistance.

fields.title: One Day Tours exceeded all our expectations!
fields.short_text: We were highly impressed by the Batalha Monastery and the guides' stories about Portuguese architecture and history. In addition to the beauty of Fatima, Batalha, Nazare, and Obidos, our guides made the trip enjoyable. We will definitely come back to you again. Perfect!

fields.title: The tour with One Day Tours was unforgettable!
fields.short_text: Obidos is such a small but atmospheric town that I had never heard of before. The guides on this tour were absolute professionals, and their stories made us fall in love with every place we saw. Ive recommended them to all my friends and family and will continue to do so!

fields.title: Recommend to everyone!
fields.short_text: I recommend visiting the One Day Tours excursion with your family! We were impressed by Nazare, where we ate fresh seafood and tried the local drink "Ginjinha de Obidos" with my husband. The guide was very likable to the children and us, as he created a friendly atmosphere and intrigued us with his stories.

fields.title: Fabulous!
fields.short_text: The One Day Tours excursion to Fatima and Obidos left vivid memories! The Batalha Monastery impressed me with its architecture and history, and I give special thanks for organizing a seafood lunch and a picturesque bonus road. Every minute of the tour was planned to perfection, and the guide became a close guide to the world of Portuguese history and culture.

fields.title: Thanks for professionalism!
fields.short_text: I was utterly impressed with the professionalism and customer service of One Day Tours. The guides introduced me to new stories about Portugal! The trip to Obidos will be remembered forever  narrow streets, Portuguese architecture, the local drink "Ginjinha de Obidos," and the atmosphere of the Middle Ages. Thank you for a fantastic experience.

fields.title: Unforgettable trip
fields.short_text: Visiting Fatima with One Day Tours was the best idea! We visited the Batalha Monastery, declared a UNESCO World Heritage Site, and learned about the best surfing spotit turns out to be in Nazare. Thanks to the guides for their interesting approach to the tour and for combining the architectural and religious side of Portugal. Fabulous!

fields.title: I recommend!
fields.short_text: One Day Tours showcased the world of Portuguese history and religion in all its splendor! The guides shared many insightful facts about Fatima and the Batalha Monastery. Time on the road with picturesque views and lunch in Nazare flew by quickly and beautifully. It was especially pleasing that our guide was not only knowledgeable but also amiable.

fields.title: Great experience with this company!
fields.short_text: The excursion with One Day Tours to Fatima and Obidos brought many positive emotions! The trip to Obidos felt like a journey through time - a cozy medieval town with mesmerizing architecture. Efficiency and punctuality are hallmarks of OneDayTour service.

fields.title: Perfect!
fields.short_text: This tour with One Day Tours immersed me in the atmosphere of the Middle Ages and religious history! I am a spiritual person, and the city of Fatima and the Batalha Monastery are very dear to me. The guide became an interesting conversationalist for me and made this trip even more enjoyable.

fields.title: It's been great experience for all of us
fields.short_text: It seems to me that Sintra and Cascais are the only places in Portugal that reveal all the royal splendor. Thanks to the organizers for a well-thought-out route with picturesque views of the Atlantic Ocean. The guides are true professionals, they know everything down to the smallest detail. Perfect!

fields.title: I am very pleased with my trip to Sintra with One Day Tours.
fields.short_text: It was my first time in this town, and I was particularly impressed by the Pena Palace. The old part of the city surprised me with the number of tasty places, thanks to the guides for their recommendations and conversation. It's evident that the staff love their job. I will definitely be using their services again in the future.

fields.title: Superb!
fields.short_text: The guides provided a lot of fascinating information about Sintra and its attractions. I'm a fan of Portugal's nature, but it was my first time on the Cabo da Roca cliff. The view from the top is incredible, and you can even see the Pena Palace, which we visited earlier.

fields.title: Super special trip
fields.short_text: Thanks to the guides for revealing secret and tasty places in the center of the Old Town of Sintra. The team is always friendly and helpful, and their products are outstanding. I've recommended them to all my friends and family, and I will continue to do so!

fields.title: 100% recommended!
fields.short_text: The moment we climbed Cabo da Roca will forever remain one of my brightest memories. I'm glad I joined the One Day Tours excursion and met the guides. They are not only interesting conversationalists but also fun guys. The journey back was accompanied by the entire coastline from Cascais to Lisbon. This must be seen firsthand.

fields.title: This trip is worth every euro!
fields.short_text: One Day Tours guides showed and told about all the attractions from Sintra to Cascais. The 8-hour tour flew by quickly and unnoticed. Recommended for a family educational vacation. I sincerely appreciate it.

fields.title: Simply the best!
fields.short_text: An excursion to Sintra and Cascais with One Day Tours is the best idea if you find yourself in Portugal. I really enjoyed the places I saw, from the mystical architecture of the Pena Palace to the picturesque view from the Cabo da Roca cliff. But I want to highlight the contribution of the One Day Tours guide.

fields.title: Thank you for your assistance!
fields.short_text: The town of Sintra surprised me with the richness of its unique places. The tour organizers perfectly combined architecture, nature, and gastronomic places in 8 hours. One Day Tours guide is fun and smart guy who told the story of the Pena Palace that you won't find on the internet. I'm very glad I conquered the summit of Cabo da Roca.

fields.title: An 8-hour tour with One Day Tours is the best gift I've ever received. The day in Sintra was filled with a variety of places, and even on the road, we saw all the beauty of the coastal towns of Cascais, Estoril, and Oeiras. The power of the ocean waves is
fields.short_text: An 8-hour tour with One Day Tours is the best gift I've ever received. The day in Sintra was filled with a variety of places, and even on the road, we saw all the beauty of the coastal towns of Cascais, Estoril, and Oeiras. The power of the ocean waves is striking when you're on top of the Cabo da Roca cliff. Thanks to the guides for the experience.

fields.title: Our family has unforgettable impressions of our trip with One Day Tours!
fields.short_text: The program was organized with attention to the smallest details. Thanks to the guides for the informative information and delicious lunch in the center of the old town of Sintra. Excellent!

fields.title: I had an amazing experience with One Day Tours!
fields.short_text: The Pena Palace looks mystical and yet royal, its architecture is stunning. The town of Sintra is very cozy; the guides showed us some tasty places there. The customer service was top-notch, and the product exceeded my expectations.

fields.title: Impressed!
fields.short_text: I was completely impressed with the professionalism and customer service at One Day Tours. The guides told us why the Pena Palace in Sintra was considered mystical and took us to the very picturesque location - Cabo da Roca. The entire road was accompanied by views of the coastal towns of Cascais, Estoril, and Oeiras. 100% recommended!

fields.title: Good trip!
fields.short_text: I didn't believe that in 8 hours, you could visit so many places and learn a bunch of unique information. One Day Tours changed my perception of excursions. These guys show Portugal from a new and exciting perspective. Pricing is fair and transparent - definitely value for money.

fields.title: Amazing
fields.short_text: The quality of One Day Tours work is exceptional, and I couldn't be happier with the final result. In addition to the program in Sintra and Cascais, we saw the true ocean nature of Portugal on the Cabo da Roca cliff. The guide provided exclusive information and places.

fields.title: Best excursion ever!
fields.short_text: Our family really enjoyed the day in Sintra with One Day Tours. The guides were friendly and professional in their stories about the Pena Palace. They told us where to eat well in the center of the Old Town and which road was the most picturesque. Next time, we'll definitely join new One Day Tours excursions.

fields.title: Thank you for your guidance!
fields.short_text: Seeing such a colossal palace on such a scale for the first time in Queluz was terrific. And the city of Sintra revealed its mystical side. The delicious lunch and Pena Palace left unforgettable impressions.

fields.title: 100% recommended!
fields.short_text: The royal architecture in the palaces of Queluz and Pena is something I haven't seen on any other tour in Portugal. Special thanks for the seafood spot by the shore and the lunch in Sintra. I learned a lot of new information from the guides.

fields.title: Thank you for a fantastic experience
fields.short_text: I visited Sintra many times before, but only here I found the best combinations of trips with Pena Palace. I wish everyone could see Portugal's surrounding nature and architecture.

fields.title: Queluz Palace
fields.short_text: Thanks to the guides for the unique information about the palaces in Sintra. I'm a fan of the Baroque style, so Queluz Palace is my top choice. If you want to immerse yourself in the atmosphere of Portugal, head to Pena Palace on this tour. Besides the sights, you'll enjoy delicious Cascais coast food.

fields.title: Thank you!!!
fields.short_text: Thanks to the guides for the exciting information and unique spots. Ive recommended them to all my friends and family and will continue to do so!

fields.title: Thank you very much guys
fields.short_text: I think this tour is the perfect opportunity to feel in the spirit of Portugal. The guide skillfully revealed places and information that few know about, like the palaces in Sintra, especially Pena on the mountaintop.

fields.title: Great driver with perfect knowledge!
fields.short_text: In my opinion, time flew by quickly and excitingly. I am a repeat customer, and they never disappoint. The team is always friendly and helpful, and their products are outstanding. Thanks for the unique locations and food by the Cascais coast.

fields.title: I will definitely be using you services again in the future.
fields.short_text: Personally, I think this tour is the best way to get to know Portugal. The guide perfectly explained the history of the architectural palaces of Pena and Queluz.

fields.title: Elegant trip
fields.short_text: The guide of this tour managed to fit the impossible into one day: fascinating information, locations with architecture and nature, and a wonderful dinner by the Cascais coast. The quality of their work is exceptional, and I couldnt be happier with the final result.

fields.title: Fabulous!
fields.short_text: Your tour, as always, impressed me. For one day, I saw royal architecture in the palaces of Pena and Queluz, the nature of Sintra, and had a great meal by the Cascais coast! Efficiency and punctuality are the visit cards of their service.

fields.title: My sincere thanks!
fields.short_text: A one-day tour with your guide is the best way to spend my birthday! You impressed me with the palaces of Queluz and Pena and the overall atmosphere of Sintra. Dinner by the Cascais coast with fresh seafood added a special touch.

fields.title: Recommend to all
fields.short_text: I had a fantastic experience with this company! The city of Sintra is far from boring; it's captivating with its palaces of Queluz and Pena, and the nature revealed at the summit. The customer service was top-notch, and the product exceeded my expectations.

fields.title: Perfect!
fields.short_text: My colleagues and I took this tour instead of a corporate event, which was genius. The city of Sintra with you brought us even closer together. Thanks for the beautiful spots by the Cascais coast, on the mountain top, and the wonderful seafood dinner.

fields.title: Great experience with family!
fields.short_text: It goes without saying that the one-day trip to Queluz Palace and Sintra surpassed all expectations! The magnificent vistas, intriguing anecdotes from the guide, and excellent food made this day unforgettable.

fields.title: Excellent!
fields.short_text: In my view, this tour sets an example for many companies. Knowledgeable and friendly guides are the key to success. Special thanks for the program on the Baroque-style palaces. Pena Palace on the mountaintop in Sintra made the biggest impression.

fields.title: Please accept my deepest thanks!
fields.short_text: The professionalism of the guide was top-notch! The Palace of Queluz, with its French gardens, is simply magnificent. Special thanks for the lunch in Ericeira, which featured fresh seafood from the ocean. We concluded the day with a visit to the Monastery of Mafra.

fields.title: Amazing
fields.short_text: This tour was like a journey through time. The guide impressed us with stories about the Queluz Palace, and the fresh seafood lunch in Ericeira was energizing. The architecture of Mafra is simply fantastic! I will definitely be using their services again in the future.

fields.title: Loved it!
fields.short_text: I can't help but share my impressions! Queluz Palace is an architectural masterpiece. In Ericeira, we enjoyed a delicious lunch of fresh seafood. The day ended surrounded by the stunning nature near the Mafra Palace. I was completely impressed with their professionalism and customer service.

fields.title: Great!
fields.short_text: The Queluz and Mafra palaces tour was the best way to spend time. The lunch of fresh seafood in Ericeira was a true culinary delight. The guide was very attentive and provided lots of interesting information.

fields.title: Experienced traveller
fields.short_text: We had a fantastic day with this tour. The Queluz and Mafra palaces are in Portuguese baroque style, and the lunch in Ericeira is simply amazing. The seafood was fresh and tasty. Thanks to the tour organizers for their high level of professionalism!

fields.title: Excelent
fields.short_text: This tour left unforgettable impressions. Queluz Palace is an accurate representation of Portugal's architecture. Thanks to the guides for their exciting stories and organization. The lunch in Ericeira was incredibly delicious. Mafra Palace was impressed with its scale and the beauty of the surrounding natural features.

fields.title: Thank you for the wonderful day and the great guide!
fields.short_text: This tour is the best in my life! The guides amazed us with facts about the magnificent Mafra Palace. I especially liked Queluz Palace architecture and French gardens.

fields.title: Fantastic!!!
fields.short_text: The excursion on this tour was simply fantastic! Queluz Palace made an incredible impression that I want to revisit again and again. I will definitely be using their services again in the future.

fields.title: I had a fantastic experience with this company!
fields.short_text: This tour is perfect for an active and educational day. The guides talked about the history of the Queluz and Mafra palaces, which was incredibly impressive. For one day, we enjoyed architecture, nature, and even gastronomy at a local bakery in Ericeira.

fields.title: We loved experience
fields.short_text: My wife and kids are thrilled with this tour. It was informative to show the kids how kings lived during the Baroque era in Queluz Palace. My wife loved the gardens and Mafra Palace. And I remembered the jokes and facts from the guide and the delicious seafood in Ericeira. Ive recommended them to all my friends and will continue to do so!

fields.title: 100% recommend!
fields.short_text: Thanks to your tour, I had a wonderful day! Thank you for an active program exploring beloved Portugal. You showed me its new architectural and mystical side. The guides told many stories that you won't find on the internet. You left unforgettable impressions!

fields.title: Perfect!
fields.short_text: My impression is that the tour encompassed the impossible. For one day, your guide showed us the historical, gastronomic, and natural sides of the small town of Sintra in Portugal. I started my acquaintance with the country with you, and I am very happy about it!

fields.title: Pricing is fair and transparent - definitely value for money.
fields.short_text: The day on the tour of the Queluz and Mafra palaces will be remembered for a lifetime! In just one day, the guides provided a lot of exciting information and showed secret places I will return to. Time flew by very quickly and productively.

fields.title: Fabulous!
fields.short_text: Id like to point out that this tour is a must-visit if you want to get acquainted with non-touristy Portugal. The tour organizers revealed the charm of the Lisbon suburbs and captivated with the history and beauty of the Queluz and Mafra palaces.

fields.title: Thank you!
fields.short_text: The tour of Ericeira gave me many positive impressions. I only had one day in Portugal and am happy I spent it with you. Thank you to the organizers for making this tour to the Convent Palace of Mafra with gastronomic stops. I enjoyed the guides' engaging stories and friendly atmosphere. I will definitely be using their services again in the future.

fields.title: Wow
fields.short_text: On my next trip to Portugal, I will definitely take your tours again. It's hard to interest me in excursions, but your organization of the places and meals impressed me. One day, I saw the coastal town of Ericeira, which had its Convent Palace of Mafra, and learned a lot of fascinating information. I especially wanted to thank you for stopping at the local bakery. Ill be back.

fields.title: Ericeira
fields.short_text: I am thrilled with the Ericeira tour. You showed me a location in Portugal that I would never find myself. Thank you so much for the stories and the time spent with you. 100% recommended!

fields.title: Mafra and Ericeira trip review
fields.short_text: Your staff feels like family. We had a great and productive day discovering a new side of Portugal. The Baroque era, royal palaces, and picturesque nature  only your tour can combine all the beautiful aspects of Portugal into one. I sincerely appreciate it.

fields.title: Day in Mafra
fields.short_text: The one-day tour was a great find. We started the day with Baroque architecture at the Convent Palace of Mafra and ended at the coast of Ericeira. It felt like the guides were my friends! We talked a lot about Portugal and ended the day eating seafood. You can safely go on this tour even without a company. Their staff is not only friendly but also highly skilled.

fields.title: It seems to me that I will miss this day in France
fields.short_text: For one day with you, I saw non-touristy places in Portugal and had great conversations with the tour guides. The coastal town of Ericeira amazed me with its nature and delicious food. I will definitely recommend you to my friends and join future trips.

fields.title: I highly recommend this company!
fields.short_text: The one-day tour to the town of Ericeira was my discovery. This tour is perfect for those who dont have much time but want to spend their free days productively. The Convent Palace with the Serco Garden is a very picturesque place. Plus, I learned a lot of exciting information.

I am a photographer, and your one-day tour in Ericeira allowed me to expand my portfolio with scenic nature shots. Thank you for adding stops along the way for taking photos. Besides the beautiful places, I learned a lot about the history of Mafra Palace. Your guides are true professionals and pleasant people to talk to.

fields.title: Very food!
fields.short_text: I went on this tour with my brother, who loves the Baroque era and ancient palaces. I was impressed by the Portuguese architecture and the history the guides discussed. In Ericeira, we had the most delicious pastries of our lives. The quality of the experiences is consistently outstanding, exceeding my expectations every time.

fields.title: We enjoyed the experience with onedaytours.pt
fields.short_text: The one-day tour to Ericeira was my discovery of active recreation that doesnt require another vacation afterward. Time flew by so quickly that I didnt even get tired. We often stopped at Mafra Palace and the Serco Garden to admire nature. The quality of their work is exceptional, and I couldnt be happier with the final result.

fields.title: Recommend!

The guides showed many beautiful places around Mafra Palace and in the town of Ericeira. Efficiency and punctuality are hallmarks of their service.

fields.title: Thank you!
fields.short_text: The one-day tour of Mafra Palace and the Ericeira Reserve are the most picturesque places Ive ever seen. Thank you to the tour organizers for what I saw and the captivating stories. Time flew by very quickly and easily. Please accept my deepest thanks.

fields.title: I recommend One Day Tours to everyone.
fields.short_text: It is a great idea for a gift or simply for spending time productively. Besides Mafra Palace and its Serco Garden, I was amazed by the scenic panorama of the town of Ericeira. Thank you for a fantastic experience.

fields.title: 5 stars all the way!
fields.short_text: Portugal is not just about Lisbon. Your guides showed unique places that not every guidebook knows. Thank you for showing and telling us about the Baroque era in the Portuguese Ericeira Reserve and adding stops for photos and lunch. Amazing!

fields.title: Absolutely amazing!
fields.short_text: The organization of this tour was excellent! You combined history, wine, and travel. I had no idea about the Jose Maria da Fonseca House Museum before. This was my first wine tasting, and Im glad it was with you! Thank you for your guidance.

fields.title: Wine tasting!
fields.short_text: Ive wanted to attend a wine tasting in Portugal for a long time. The wine tasting was not only delicious but also educational with your guides. The trip went by quickly and beautifully, especially crossing Lisbon's iconic bridges. Perfect!

fields.title: 5 stars experience!

fields.title: I highly recommend this company!
fields.short_text: Every detail of this tour was thought out to perfection. From the departure to the return to Lisbon, time flew by smoothly. Besides the sights, our guide shared many stories about the Jose Maria da Fonseca winery, enriching the wine-tasting experience.

fields.title: From the moment I contacted them, they were responsive and accommodating.
fields.short_text: I was impressed by the Jose Maria da Fonseca winery. Thank you for planning every minute and filling the day with pleasant experiences. I cant say enough good things about the company.

fields.title: Amazing

fields.title: Super experience!
fields.short_text: I had a great time. Thanks to the fun and interesting guide, who brought the tour group together and showed us the beauty of the Jose Maria da Fonseca winery. The staff is not only friendly but also highly skilled.

fields.title: Best experience on my trip

The wine tasting featured various kinds and a great selection to purchase. I will definitely be using their services again in the future.

fields.title: The tour to Jose Maria da Fonseca was a fantastic experience for me.
fields.short_text: On the way to Setubal, the guides introduced us to the winery's history, and we crossed Lisbon's iconic bridges. The scenic drive and variety of wines brightened my day. My thanks and appreciation.

fields.title: If you love wine - this tour is for you!
fields.short_text: The Jose Maria da Fonseca winery and wine tasting are an excellent way to spend a day enjoying and learning. Our guide made this trip fun and exciting. Please accept my deepest thanks.

fields.title: Best day of vacation
fields.short_text: The one-day tour to the Jose Maria da Fonseca winery was an unforgettable event during our trip to Portugal. The wine tasting was delicious and even more enjoyable with the guides. Be prepared to take home several bottles of wine. Simply the best!

fields.title: 5 stars trip
fields.short_text: On the way to Jose Maria da Fonseca, the guides shared fascinating history about the winery and took us over Lisbons bridges. My introduction to Portugal started on a very positive note. Thanks to the guides, the trip was fun and easy from beginning to end.

fields.title: Perfect!
fields.short_text: One Day Tours exceeded all my expectations. On this day, I learned and saw more than I had on all my previous trips to Portugal. Thank you to the tour organizers for the program and knowledge about the Jose Maria da Fonseca winery.

fields.title: Recommend!

The team is always friendly and helpful, and their products are outstanding. Ive recommended them to all my friends and family and will continue to do so!

I really liked the level of service in everything. Everything on time, clean, polite and friendly staff, absolutely worth the price! I recommend you try it, you will have a pleasant experience.
I liked the food, competent and experienced guide, comfortable conditions of the trip.

Highly recommended! I truly enjoyed Lisbon's downtown walking tour. The guides are professional and funny. The itinerary is well-thought to the smallest detail. I had a short time in Lisbon but could fit in uncountable impressions thanks to the One Day Tours team. Wish you growth and thankful clients!:)

Great! One Day Tours team has given me and my family a perfect experience. We've ordered the tour to Sintra&Cascais and got unforgettable impressions of the most amazing spots of Portugal. I can't wait to go on the next adventure. 100% recommend it!

Awesome! I found everything I needed with the One Day Tours trip to Fatima. If you're looking for tranquility and spirituality, this experience is the perfect option.  Additionally, I wanna highlight great communication and customer service. I'll come back, thank you, guys:)

My journey with One Day Tours to Comporta was spectacular! If you've already seen all the major tourist attractions, choose this option to see the pristine beauty of Portugal. Time on the road flies fast thanks to the comfortable vehicles and friendly atmosphere. 100% unforgettable adventure.

Thank you, OneDayTours, for an adventure I'll never forget. Together with my husband we booked an experience to the iconic surfing sport of Portugal, combined with the most popular coastal cities, Peniche and Nazare, and got a great opportunity to see Portugal off the beaten paths. Don't miss your chance to try it!

Exceptional experience for foodies with One Day Tours. While traveling in Portugal, I got an authentic taste of the country from savoring wine in Setubal to exploring hidden spots of the region, every moment was a delight. I can't wait to embark on other adventures. Love it!

fields.title: Price Match Policy
fields.content:
At One Day Tours Portugal, we guarantee the lowest prices on our travel product range! We constantly compare One Day Tours Portugal prices to our competitors' prices to make sure that we make the best offer.

If you find a better price on any similar product available from another travel company operating in Portugal, we'll be happy to match it!

Our Price Match Policy ensures that you receive exceptional value for your tour bookings. Here's how it works:

  1. Eligibility: Our Price Match Policy applies to identical tour packages available from competitor tour operators within a specified radius of our locations. The tour package must be available for booking and meet all relevant criteria.
  2. Verification: To request a price match, customers must provide proof of the lower price from the competitor, such as a current advertisement, brochure, or website link. The details of the tour package must match exactly.
  3. Qualifying Criteria: The price-matched tour package must be identical in destination, duration, itinerary, inclusions, and quality to the one offered by OneDayTours. We do not match the price of the discounted or promotional codes, group rates, or special membership prices.
  4. Exclusions: Our Price Match Policy does not apply to experiences that are part of limited-time promotions, flash sales, last-minute deals, or exclusive offers. We also do not match prices from auction or marketplace sites.
  5. Price Adjustment: If the customer meets all eligibility criteria and provides valid verification, we will match the competitor's price at the time of booking or refund the difference if the tour was recently booked with us.
  6. Competitor's Price: The competitor's price must be in the local currency and include any applicable taxes, fees, and surcharges. We reserve the right to verify the competitor's price and adjust accordingly.
  7. Discretion: One Day Tours Portugal reserves the right to decline a price match if it would result in a loss for the company or if the competitor's price is below our cost.

If you have any questions or would like to request a price match, please contact our customer support team for assistance at support@onedaytours.pt.

One Day Tours Portugal reserves the right to modify or terminate this policy at any time without prior notification.
